{"tid":1540133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Breaking] Five demands, NO ONE LESS","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T16:28:49.000Z","uid":199200,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff61a5251e69ab8463f60bba46a03219f0ba2be","tid":1540133,"uid":199200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:53:25.000Z","msg":"To all foreign friends: a few minutes ago, Carrie Lam completely withdrew the extradition bill. This may seems to be a win for us, but she only managed to met ONE of our five demands. Our five demands are:<br />\n1. Withdrawal of the extradition bill from the legislative process <br />\n2. Retraction of the characterisation of the protests as &quot;riots&quot;<br />\n3. Release and exoneration of arrested protesters<br />\n4. Establishment of an independent commission of inquiry into police behaviour<br />\n5. Universal suffrage for Legislative Council and Chief Executive election<br />\nWith reference with one of our slogan: five demands, no one less, we shall fight on until all our demands had been met. The withdrawal of the bill would not stop us from fighting for freedom.<br />\n<br />\nFive demands, no one less. 五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"8b5dc210b27d28377567264b5d936fa31d746a84","tid":1540133,"uid":199200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:53:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"307db854ebbc026831d2c39f8acfe5744130a691","tid":1540133,"uid":199200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:53:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6d3ca8589d5164bed1b9238ecc33dc319c6a8e94","tid":1540133,"uid":199200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:53:51.000Z","msg":"NO ONE LESS!"},{"pid":"98e85026a84fea14045ad73e6964464afc41cbcf","tid":1540133,"uid":199200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:54:05.000Z","msg":"NO ONE LESS!"},{"pid":"e4aaf6d7d1b64fcd2dc037598edf1afd58a73921","tid":1540