Time":"2019-09-04T11:09:54.000Z","msg":"bump! Wholeheartedly agree with this, and some of the responses. <br />\n<br />\nOf course, we want her to respond and meet the 5 key demands, thus just catering for the withdrawal does not mean the it is resolved. <br />\n<br />\nSecondly, she didn't say that it is an executive decision. If she follows up and says that we will put the withdrawal decision before the legislative council, and then the voting outcome becomes a rejection for the withdrawal, then we haven't made any progress."},{"pid":"0efe5e87c5245410ccd45c83115155ae4b408b0f","tid":1540133,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:10:23.000Z","msg":"here is the scenario:<br />\n<br />\n- You demand one bill to be retracted. <br />\n<strong>- the Gov said no, we arent going the say the &quot;r&quot; word</strong><br />\n- You kept on asking<br />\n- the Gov sent the Police to beat you up to death<br />\n- 7 lives gone, 1 is missing, ~1200 arrested, 2 eyeballs were lost.<br />\n- We rised 4 extra demands because of what the Gov did<br />\n- the US is going to pass the HK Human Rights and Democracy Act<br />\n<br />\n<strong>- the Gov &quot;Oh shit we are going to take this bill down (not R-word) totally&quot;</strong><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: gold;\">And we are going back and pretend nothing happed? After all these? </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">See for youself:  there is no time to celebrate. </span>"},{"pid":"7b738d5e3b37c6e8d1dd4938350cccef1ced24d6","tid":1540133,"uid":287508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:11:17.000Z","msg":"Five demands, not one less<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8 people committed suicide during the past 3 months, and over 1k arrested.<br />\n<br />\nThe problem has shifted from anti bill amendment to the HKSAR government that are acting against HKers interests. We can&rsquo;t and won&rsquo;t back down!<br />\n<br />\nCarrie Lam can&rsquo;t win if we stay strong and united. Let the war begin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba921f461d3ae0d87d2faa5149884a9438623e20","tid":1540133,"uid":15193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65de4de7eb383d00aab77b5b3d7d7cadc2c5845","tid":1540133,"uid":287508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:12:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ff8137521d9862539b54993a77b49d39cc181a4b","tid":1540133,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:13:01.000Z","msg":"pump"},{"pid":"729407c3de7d443dd79680cb4a50c67386284cf5","tid":1540133,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:13:44.000Z","msg":"actually carrie lam is a liar,  hong kong citizens can't believe her words until the procedure of withdrawing the bill start.<br />\n<br />\nand she never explain about the police state which is important for the safety of hong kong!!!"},{"pid":"a1f5ee5eee164df06b92f456a70489c30b2de8bc","tid":1540133,"uid":13349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:13:51.000Z","msg":"no one less<br />\nsee you on sunday"},{"pid":"65ca60bfb3dcd6337adc713134f7efc1337d6605","tid":1540133,"uid":199200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:14:34.000Z","msg":"The unnecessary violence used by the police had caused three eyeballs losses, bone cracks and sexual assault on arrestees. By confessing to such concession would be a shame to ourselves."},{"pid":"7df866423b2875e0a9d6136fe6ba991569665d9a","tid":1540133,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"敵疲我打，敵退我追!!"},{"pid":"e21d6eb4d31940468d4155bb4dcf08bf6e29ae0e","tid":1540133,"uid":199200,"like":0,"dislike":